ABOUT.TITLE: About
ABOUT.PROLOG: To research your project by using this tool you should:
ABOUT.3a: In the absence of a sufficient number of points needed to find people those who are willing to perform the test they should get it. This is done by being a participant in the usability test of their application and sending the generated data and judgments, then this person gives us credit for a well done job.
ABOUT.3b: If the user account contains the correct assessment of the number of points to find people willing to perform the test, you can create a new project.
ABOUT.4e: Range of points for respondent, max used points can't be greater than your points
ABOUT.4f: Set configs additional parameters like add comment field, star rating to all steps.
ABOUT.5: After receiving responses preview the responses from respondents. Watch videos by using achromatic view and stop to log actions.
ABOUT.6: Get data and and use it to make results.
ABOUT.7: Give points for respondents to help.
